timeline.bodyText:
Technically, the license level check is just licenseState.checkFeature, so I'd prefer to have the logic as
if (compositeAuditTrail.isEmpty() == false && licenseState.isSecurityEnabled()) {
    if (licenseState.checkFeature(Feature.SECURITY_AUDITING)) {
    }
}

which is more accurate to the warning message.

